text: Mohammad Ghazi al-Jalali (born 22 March 1969) is a Syrian civil engineer and politician. He was the head of the Syrian caretaker government for a few days in December 2024. He was the Prime Minister from 14 September 2024 to 9 December 2024. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Syria
title: Mohammad Ghazi al-Jalali
